TMC Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for Adhoc Assistant Professor E Posts
Prasanna / All Government Jobs / Aug 18, 2025, 14:16 IST
 Tata Memorial Centre
 1 Jobs |  Posted On : 18-Aug-2025 |  Maharashtra |  Salary : 128,000 to 140,000




FOLLOW

Tata Memorial Centre (TMC) has announced the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for Adhoc Assistant Professor E Positions. Those candidates who have qualified in the MD, DNB can grab this chance and apply for these posts. Here, we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for the TMC Recruitment 2025. Interested and eligible candidates can attend the interview at the address given below. For more details, visit the official website.




If you are looking for more, here is a list of Government Jobs in 2025 that you can all apply for. Use this link for more jobs in Maharashtra.

TMC Recruitment 2025 - Eligibility Criteria
Name of the Posts	No. of Vacancies	Qualification
Adhoc Assistant Professor E	01	MD, DNB

Age Limit for the TMC Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Age Limit: 21 years.
The Maximum Age Limit: 45 years.

Selection Process for the TMC Recruitment 2025

Interview

Salary Structure for the TMC Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Salary: Rs. 1,28,000 /- per month.
The Maximum Salary: Rs. 1,40,000 /- per month.

Application fee for the TMC Recruitment 2025

There is no application fee.
How to Apply for the TMC Recruitment 2025
Visit the official website.
Go to the recruitment or career page.
Check for the Adhoc Assistant Professor Jobs 2025.
Read the notification carefully.
Check the eligibility criteria.
If you meet the eligibility criteria.
Then, attend the interview at the address given below.

Venue

Meeting Room, 3rd Floor, Main Building, Tata Memorial Hospital, Dr. E. Borges Road, Parel, Mumbai – 400012  

Important Dates

Date of Walk-in-Interview	26-08-2025
